text: Koprivnički Ivanec is a municipality in the Koprivnica-Križevci County in Croatia. According to the 2001 census, there are 2,361 inhabitants in the area, with Croats forming an absolute majority. ==History== In the late 19th century and 20th century, Koprivnički Ivanec was part of the Varaždin County of the Kingdom of Croatia-Slavonia.
